"如要创建模型，前往 :menuselection:`会计 --> 配置 --> 递延费用模型`，点击*创建*并按与创建新分录相同的方法填写表单。"

#: ../../accounting/payables/supplier_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:150
msgid ""
"You can also convert a *confirmed Deferred Expense entry* into a model by "
