"Defining Payment Terms automates the computation of payments due dates, both"
" for invoices and bills. This is particularly helpful in managing "
"installment plans."
msgstr "定义付款条件可以自动计算发票和账单的付款到期日。这对管理分期付款计划特别有用。"

